{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-156","title":"焦虑烦躁","sectionId":"chapter-07","sectionTitle":"喜怒哀乐听你说","pageStart":787,"pageEnd":791,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":23,"duplicateEntryCount":17,"pages":[{"number":787,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"156 焦虑烦躁"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"unrest [ʌnˈrest]","headword":"unrest"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.不安，动荡"},{"type":"entry","text":"anxious [ˈæŋkʃəs]","headword":"anxious"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.忧虑的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎be anxious about担忧/be anxious for为…而焦虑/feel anxious变得着急"},{"type":"entry","text":"harassment [ˈhærəsmənt]","headword":"harassment"}]},{"number":788,"blocks":[{"type":"definition","text":"n.烦恼"},{"type":"entry","text":"worrying [ˈwʌriɪŋ]","headword":"worrying"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.令人担忧的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎worrying situation令人忧心的情势"},{"type":"entry","text":"troubled [ˈtrʌbld]","headword":"troubled"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.烦恼的"},{"type":"entry","text":"disturbing [dɪˈstɜːbɪŋ]","headword":"disturbing"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.令人不安的"},{"type":"entry","text":"uneasy [ʌnˈiːzi]","headword":"uneasy"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.不自在的，不安的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎be uneasy about担忧"},{"type":"entry","text":"nervous [ˈnɜːvəs]","headword":"nervous"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.紧张不安的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎get nervous紧张不安"},{"type":"entry","text":"restless [ˈrestləs]","headword":"restless"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.不安的，焦躁的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎restless heart不安的心"}]},{"number":789,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"fretful [ˈfretfl]","headword":"fretful"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.烦躁的"},{"type":"entry","text":"intranquil [ɪnˈtræŋkwɪl]","headword":"intranquil"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.不安的"},{"type":"entry","text":"worry [ˈwʌri]","headword":"worry"},{"type":"definition","text":"n./v.担心（强调焦虑、烦恼或深深不安）"},{"type":"note","text":"◎worry about为…而担忧"},{"type":"entry","text":"bother [ˈbɒðə(r)]","headword":"bother"}]},{"number":790,"blocks":[{"type":"definition","text":"v.烦扰，打扰"},{"type":"note","text":"◎bother about为…烦恼"},{"type":"entry","text":"perturb [pəˈtɜːb]","headword":"perturb"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.打扰，扰乱"},{"type":"entry","text":"upset [ʌpˈset]","headword":"upset"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使心烦"},{"type":"entry","text":"live on one's nerves 总是紧张","headword":"live on one's nerves"},{"type":"entry","text":"a bundle of nerves 神经紧张","headword":"a bundle of nerves"},{"type":"entry","text":"get on one's nerves 使某人心烦","headword":"get on one's nerves"}]},{"number":791,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"give some cause for concern 令人非常担心","headword":"give some cause for concern"},{"type":"entry","text":"on one's mind 挂在心头，使人担心","headword":"on one's mind"},{"type":"entry","text":"concern about 对…表示担心/忧虑","headword":"concern about"},{"type":"entry","text":"out of your element 不适应环境","headword":"out of your element"},{"type":"entry","text":"a fish out of water 浑身不自在","headword":"a fish out of water"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：If you feel uncomfortable, please let us know. （如果您感到不"},{"type":"text","text":"适，请告诉我们。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Thanks, I am just a little tired. （谢谢，我只是有点累了。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：As she spoke we could see that she was in a fret. （她讲话时，我"},{"type":"text","text":"们看得出她很烦躁。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：What's wrong with her?（她怎么了？）"}]}]}